      </prefercite>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_69899e4286796865992610ff3eb07118">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Original audiovisual materials, as well as preservation and duplicating masters, may not be played. Researchers must consult use copies, or if none exist must pay for a use copy, which is retained by the repository. Researchers wishing to obtain an additional copy for their personal use should consult Copying Services information on the Manuscripts and Archives web site.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_a7de335f2b70ab1176d8b71a19502933">
